 on a real dataset that combines on-line user search logs\nand airline flight bookings. Experimental results show that the proposed model\noutperforms the traditional MNL model on several metrics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Mar 2018 19:55:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-19"}
