ems is driven by the Pauli principle and\nits selection of the correct collective coordinates in the form of N-body\nnormal modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Mar 2018 19:58:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-19"}
